data.description: Welcome to Brentwood Estates, where convenience meets comfort in this eco-friendly home with paid off solar panels! This adorable 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home gives you a warm welcome as you walk into a beautiful open floor plan. Straight back, set your eyes on stunning barn doors that lead right into your very own office. Work with the family, or close the doors and enjoy the view through glass doors leading to the backyard.The kitchen, with its bright white cabinets and ample storage space, offers a window over the sink for a view and extra sunshine. The laundry room doubles up as a mudroom with pantry/storage and leads straight to the attached garage. The master bedroom at the back comes with a spa-like en-suite, boasting a jetted tub and a separate walk-in shower.Take a step outside to your screened-in patio and fully fenced backyard, creating your own private retreat. Tucked away in a quiet neighborhood, Brentwood Estates is just a breezy 20-minute drive from Tyndall and less than 10 minutes from the bustling shopping scene on 23rd St. Get ready to enjoy the perfect mix of friendly vibes and convenience in your new home sweet home!
